CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Allarity Therapeutics Inc is a clinical-stage, precision medicine company. The company is actively advancing a pipeline of in-licensed oncology therapeutics for patients with difficult-to-treat cancers. Its Drug Response Predictor (DRP) technology refines patient selection and improve clinical outcomes. Its pipeline product includes Dovitinib, Stenoparib, Ixempra, and other formulations.
